1
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:44,039
Jiang Lai and Sheng Yuanzhou

2
00:00:45,159 --> 00:00:46,399
So that's the kind of relationship they have

3
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:51,200
Looks like you don't like me in this dress

4
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,159
I'll change it

5
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,079
It really is her

6
00:01:11,439 --> 00:01:12,920
Should've brought it with me

7
00:01:13,239 --> 00:01:14,319
You actually found out

8
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,519
You sent me the message

9
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,439
What do you want

10
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:25,400
Mess with you

11
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,120
Just have a little fun

12
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,519
You said I'm trashy

13
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,439
You look down on me

14
00:01:31,239 --> 00:01:32,000
And I'm pissed

15
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:34,319
So I had to get it back somewhere else

16
00:01:36,319 --> 00:01:36,680
Tell me

17
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,920
In what way am I worse than Lin Siqi

18
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:41,079
My body, my looks

19
00:01:41,359 --> 00:01:41,840
My abilities

20
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,680
Even my wealth

21
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:46,560
My family is much better off

22
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,879
Didn't think you were the jealous type, Jiang Lai

23
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,519
In our circle

24
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:52,120
A fling is pretty normal, isn't it

25
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,879
A fling

26
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:02,120
He doesn't know what we really are

27
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,040
I'm warning you

28
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,759
Don't play this kind of joke on me again

29
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,240
My patience has limits

30
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:15,319
Let me remind you

31
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,080
I'm not the only one watching you

32
00:02:19,439 --> 00:02:20,680
My guess was right

33
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,840
This is getting more and more interesting

34
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,039
Mr. Sheng

35
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,319
This is the guy who

36
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:07,879
followed you and Ms. Lin Siqi that day

37
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,560
His name is Liu Dazhuang

38
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,599
He's unemployed

39
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,919
Liu Dazhuang

40
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,520
Liu Dazhuang used to be a pro boxer

41
00:03:14,039 --> 00:03:15,680
After an injury, he retired and fell apart

42
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:16,599
He drank all day

43
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:17,400
Had a nasty temper

44
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,120
His wife couldn't take it and ran off

45
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,400
Leaving their young daughter with him

46
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:23,520
But due to his neglect

47
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:26,039
So she died of illness in her teens

48
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:28,639
Liu Dazhuang couldn't accept her death

49
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,120
He went to the hospital and caused a scene

50
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:32,159
And stabbed his daughter's attending physician

51
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:34,680
Got 9 years and 6 months for Intentional Assault

52
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,240
He was just released

53
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:38,960
Lin Siqi's mom was her attending physician

54
00:03:39,159 --> 00:03:39,400
Yes

55
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,680
Did you find his address

56
00:03:43,199 --> 00:03:45,439
He's been at his old place since he got out

57
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:06,360
The number you dialed is busy

58
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:10,240
I'm almost there

59
00:04:34,959 --> 00:04:36,040
Zhang Xiaobei, get in

60
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,480
Lin Siqi's been taken

61
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,439
He did it on purpose

62
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,319
To shake us off

63
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,319
Then what do we do

64
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:56,000
Why are you on the phone right now

65
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,519
Shut up

66
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,079
I don't care how you do it

67
00:05:02,079 --> 00:05:03,000
Within ten minutes

68
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:03,639
find me a

69
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:05,160
vehicle with the license plate Hai BF0304,

70
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,040
a Jinbei van

71
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:27,560
Hello

72
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,160
We've got the exact location

73
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:30,720
I've sent it to your phone

74
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:35,839
I've notified the police

75
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:38,800
Mr. Sheng, you don't need to go yourself

76
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:39,920
What if...

77
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,879
I'll handle it myself

78
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:00,160
Uncle Liu

79
00:06:00,279 --> 00:06:02,319
Liu Xia wasn't killed by my mom

80
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,639
She died from illness

81
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:05,480
My mom and I were devastated too

82
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,120
Shut up

83
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:07,959
It was obviously a misdiagnosis

84
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,399
Xiaxia was perfectly healthy

85
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,879
Our place was cold in winter

86
00:06:15,279 --> 00:06:16,360
Even without a stove

87
00:06:17,079 --> 00:06:18,199
she never felt cold

88
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,800
And she never got sick

89
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,360
She did get cold, and she did get sick

90
00:06:23,519 --> 00:06:24,839
You just didn't notice

91
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,800
Bullshit

92
00:06:31,199 --> 00:06:32,759
Don't try to blame me

93
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,079
All of you said

94
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:35,480
that I killed my daughter

95
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,879
That I caused her to get sick

96
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,439
I loved her

97
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,519
I loved her more than anything

98
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,920
I'll prove it to you today

99
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,800
How much I loved her

100
00:07:02,399 --> 00:07:03,279
If you rush in like that

101
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,399
What if you set him off

102
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:05,839
So we just wait here for the cops

103
00:07:05,959 --> 00:07:07,240
What if he suddenly attacks

104
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,720
Calm down. Here's what we do

105
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:10,319
You rush in

106
00:07:10,759 --> 00:07:11,720
And grab his attention

107
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:12,839
I'll go get her out

108
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:14,199
If things get dangerous

109
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:14,959
you run first

110
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,240
Staying alive comes first

111
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,600
You hear me

112
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,199
Stay calm

113
00:07:19,959 --> 00:07:20,480
Go

114
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:26,199
Xiaxia

115
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,480
Daddy's gonna avenge you today

116
00:07:50,839 --> 00:07:52,199
Snap out of it, Uncle Liu

117
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:54,439
Liu Xia wouldn't want to see you like this

118
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,160
Weren't you two good friends

119
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:58,079
Perfect, you can go keep her company

120
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,120
And atone for your mom while you're at it

121
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,160
Who's there

122
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,360
It's me

123
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,319
I'm the security guard

124
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:22,160
Xiaobei

125
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:24,839
I heard some noise over here

126
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,079
What's going on

127
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:29,439
Security

128
00:08:29,959 --> 00:08:30,439
Yeah

129
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,800
No one's managed this place in ages

130
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:32,879
Why is there security

131
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,600
Our company just bought this land

132
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,159
We have to patrol every day

133
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:41,679
To prevent anyone from stealing these materials

134
00:08:41,879 --> 00:08:42,159
Don't be scared

135
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:45,519
I heard some residents reported recently

136
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:47,159
that there's a suspicious person around here

137
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:48,120
How about this

138
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,879
Come with me to the security office

139
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,480
Let's get your info registered, all right

140
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:53,159
Let's go

141
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,279
Let's go

142
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,120
Get out of here, now

143
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,000
Hurry, get out of here

144
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,720
The car's outside! Hurry

145
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,600
Xiaobei

146
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:06,159
Hurry

147
00:09:21,039 --> 00:09:21,919
Hurry

148
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:47,159
Liu Dazhuang has been brought to justice

149
00:09:47,559 --> 00:09:48,120
We'll take care of it

150
00:09:48,519 --> 00:09:49,480
Pick a time tomorrow

151
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,759
Come to the station to give a statement

152
00:09:53,399 --> 00:09:53,840
Thank you

153
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:54,840
Thank you

154
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:13,039
Thanks for what you did just now

155
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,320
I'm just glad you're okay

156
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:20,240
Did your family have a grudge against Liu Dazhuang

157
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,600
But it was all a misunderstanding

158
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:28,600
I met Liu Xia when we were little

159
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:29,720
At Jiang Lai's house

160
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,720
Jiang Lai's house

161
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:35,240
Uncle Liu was the gatekeeper there at the time

162
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:37,840
And Liu Xia would stay in the guardhouse

163
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:40,440
My mom was Jiang Lai's attending physician

164
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:42,720
So she took me with her on house calls

165
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:45,840
The three of us were about the same age

166
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:46,759
And we were all girls

167
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,399
So we started playing together right away

168
00:10:48,919 --> 00:10:51,000
Your mom was Jiang Lai's attending physician

169
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:54,200
So the one Liu Dazhuang stabbed was...

170
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,840
It was my mom

171
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,799
Uncle Liu firmly believed back then

172
00:10:59,799 --> 00:11:01,039
that my mom misdiagnosed her

173
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,639
and that's what got Liu Xia killed

174
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,799
So he rushed to the hospital

175
00:11:06,039 --> 00:11:06,919
and stabbed her

176
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:09,519
But my mom still signed a Letter of forgiveness

177
00:11:10,279 --> 00:11:11,200
Because she said

178
00:11:11,799 --> 00:11:13,480
he was just a grieving,

179
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:15,279
pitiful father

180
00:11:18,679 --> 00:11:19,679
You and your mom

181
00:11:20,639 --> 00:11:21,720
are both really gentle people

182
00:11:26,679 --> 00:11:28,879
Why does Sheng Yuanzhou care about me so much

183
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,639
The two of them have changed so much lately

184
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:40,600
Xiaobei

185
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,879
Why don't you care about what happens to me

186
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:49,440
But why was Liu Dazhuang so sure

187
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:50,879
that your mom misdiagnosed her

188
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,600
That's the strange part

189
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:55,840
Jiang Lai had leukemia back then

190
00:11:56,039 --> 00:11:57,480
They'd already issued a Critical condition notice

191
00:11:57,799 --> 00:11:59,120
Then one day she suddenly got better

192
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:01,159
But while she was recovering

193
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:03,320
Liu Xia suddenly came down with leukemia

194
00:12:04,279 --> 00:12:05,159
and died

195
00:12:05,679 --> 00:12:07,559
While one person's illness improved

196
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:09,559
another got the same disease and died

197
00:12:09,679 --> 00:12:10,759
They were the same age

198
00:12:10,759 --> 00:12:11,639
and the same gender

199
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:13,639
Could it be...

200
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:15,000
that Liu Xia used the Key of Fate too

201
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,799
and exchanged fates
